Yi tsoran gimmicks na lambu da ke da kyau
Zai iya zama abin kunya ga masanin kimiyya na shuka don yarda, amma ni cikakken sucker ne don gimmick lambu.
Ina so in yi tunanin shi ne saboda ina budewa ko watakila kawai ba daidai ba ne, musamman yadda abubuwa da yawa a cikin duniyar tsire-tsire suna da mahimmanci.
Amma ba ni jin kunyar in ce na fadi ga da dama daga cikinsu a tsawon rayuwa a cikin al'aura.
Duk da yake na yi imani da darajar ƙoƙarin ƙoƙari don kanka, idan ba ka tunanin koyon hanya mai wuya, ga wasu daga cikin gimmicks na yau da kullum da na zo a fadin.
Da farko, kuma mai yiwuwa mafi munin laifi, tsire-tsire tumatiri-dankalin turawa.
An yi amfani da shi a matsayin juyin juya halin nasara, tsire-tsire tumatir a kan tushen dankalin turawa shine, a gaskiya ma, tsohuwar makaranta mai son sani, wanda ya koma akalla 1920s.
Kamar yadda suke duka daga wannan iyali kuma suna da irin wannan “ƙwaƙwalwar ciki,” hakika zaka iya ƙirƙirar irin wannan al'adun da aka inganta.
Amma a nan ne matsalar: samar da kayan aiki mai mahimmanci kamar 'ya'yan itatuwa da asalinsu yana ɗaukar nauyin makamashi na rayuwa, kuma idan tsire-tsire suna ƙoƙarin yin duka iyakokin makamashi ba zai yiwu ba.
Wannan yana nufin amfanin gona na waɗannan tsire-tsire masu tsire-tsire suna da mummunar kuma babu wani abu kamar abin da kake gani a cikin hotunan tallace-tallace.
Sa'an nan kuma akwai gaskiyar cewa amfanin gona suna girma a nau'i daban-daban, don haka don girbi spuds dole ka kashe tsire-tsire kafin tumatir su yi bore.
