Kotu ta sanya wuta a lokacin zanga-zanga a California
OAKLAND, Ca. — Masu zanga-zanga a California sun sanya wuta ga wani gidan kotu, sun lalata wata tashar 'yan sanda da kuma kai wa jami'an hari bayan wata zanga-zangar lumana ta kara tsananta a daren ranar Asabar, 'yan sandan Oakland suka ce.
Masu zanga-zanga sun karya tagogi, sun fesa fentin zane, sun harba wasan wuta da kuma nuna lasers a jami'ai, sashen Oakland ya ce a Twitter.
Yawancin tweets sunyi kira don zaman lafiya kuma sun tambayi masu shirya su “taimaka mana mu samar da wurare masu aminci da wurare masu aminci ga masu zanga-zanga.”
Zanga-zangar ta fara tun jiya Asabar da yamma tare da kungiyoyi irin su “Wall of Homs,” mai kama da wata kungiya da ta kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fuskanci kashe jami'an Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan birnin don tsare wani gidan kotun tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya aike da wakilan tarayya domin su matsa kauri a kan zanga-zangar da ta auku cikin dare tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Zanga-zangar a Oakland ta fara cikin kwanciyar hankali, amma ta juya tashin hankali daga baya cikin dare.
Wani “taro ba bisa ka'ida ba” da 'yan sanda suka bayyana da misalin karfe 11:30 na dare kuma jami'ai sun bukaci jama'a su tarwatse.
Wutar ta barke ne a karamar hukumar Alameda County Superthouse kuma tana dauke ne da dan gajeren lokaci daga baya, kantunan labarai sun ruwaito.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zanga a wani wuri suna “karya tagogi da kuma canza launin fata a mazauna.”
Hotuna tweeted da sashen ya nuna fashewar gilashi da fenti da aka shanya a wani ginin 'yan sanda.
Tsauraran Tsaro Gabatarwa a wajen Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu, China
An sami tsauraran tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu, na China Lahadi, kamar yadda ma'aikatan Amurka suka shirya barin wurin.
An ga manyan motoci masu motsi guda uku sun shiga cikin ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda masu sintiri da masu tufafi suka yi layi a bangarorin biyu na titin, wadanda aka yi layi da shingayen karfe.
Editan jaridar China ta Global Times tabloid tweeted cewa an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu sa'o'i 72 a rufe, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga Yuli.
China ta yi zargin cewa wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin Chengdu suna “gudanar da ayyukan ba daidai ba ne tare da gano su.”
Ba tare da bayar da cikakken bayani ba, kakakin ma'aikatar harkokin wajen China, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya katse a harkokin China kuma ya cutar da sha'anin tsaro.
An bayar da umurnin China na rufe ofishin jakadancin a Chengdu ranar jumma'a a karrama wani umurnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin da ke Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China ta rufe ofishin Houston “domin kare kadarorin Amurka da bayanan sirri na Amurka.”
Kamar yadda rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin a Houston ya yi tasiri a ranar Juma'a, wasu gungun maza da suka bayyana a matsayin jami'an Amurka an ga gawawwaki zuwa makaman ta wata kofar baya.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar cewa ya keta yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da China za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da fayyace yadda ba.
Rushewar lokaci ya kara haifar da tashin hankali tsakanin kasashen biyu game da al'amurra daga kasuwanci da masana'antu zuwa 'yancin ɗan adam.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban 'yan bindigar Pakistan ne suka kai hari a Afghanistan
ISLAMBAD — Wani rahoton U.N. yace fiye da 'yan ta'addan Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi akasari daga cikin kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan da aka kama da alhakin kai hare haren sojan Pakistan da fararen hula.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon yace kungiyar, wacce aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta danganta ta da kungiyar Afghanistan mai alaka da kungiyar Islamic State.
Wasu daga cikin 'yan kungiyar TTP sun ma shiga kungiyar mayakan IS, wadda ke da hedikwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan bata amsa ba ranar Lahadi ga bukatar da jaridar Associated Press ta gabatar domin sharhi.
Rahoton yace IS a Afghanistan, da aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta yi ta bugun wuya ga jami'an tsaron Afghanistan har ma da dakarun Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wani lokaci da mayakan Taliban na Afghanistan suka kwace.
An shirya rahoton ne daga kungiyar bincike da sanya ido ta U.N., wadda ke bibiyar kungiyoyin ta'addanci a fadin duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta membobin IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ke ficewa, har yanzu IS na kirga tsakanin shugabanninta wani dan kasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce kungiyar sa ido ta samu bayanan cewa manyan kwamandojin kungiyar Musulunci biyu, Abu Quatibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraki, kwanan nan sun isa Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
“Kodayake a cikin rudanin yankuna, (Jihar Musulunci) ta kasance tana iya gudanar da hare-hare masu zurfi a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Hakan na nufin janyo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka,” in ji rahoton, yana nufin wata yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta sanya hannu da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
Wannan yarjejeniyar da aka kulla don baiwa Amurka damar kawo karshen shigarta shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma yayi kira ga Taliban ta bada tabbacin yankinta ba zasu yi amfani da kungiyoyin ta'addanci ba.
Ana kuma sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta bayar da tabbacin mayakan Taliban na fitar da hanu a yaki da IS.
Na biyu kuma watakila bangare mafi mahimmanci na yarjejeniyar ya yi kira ga tattaunawa tsakanin 'yan Taliban da na Kabul.
A maraicen Asabar, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta bayar da wata sanarwa tana cewa wakilin zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake rufewa ta yankin da ke neman tsallakawa fara wadancan tattaunawa, wanda aka dakatar da shi akai-akai yayin da bangarorin biyu suka yi wuf kan shirin sakin fursunoni.
Kungiyar da ke goyon bayan Amurka ta yi kira ga gwamnatin Afghanistan ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000 da Taliban ta 'yantar da ma'aikatan gwamnati 1,000 da sojoji a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawan nufin karimci gaba da tattaunawa.
Kawo yanzu dai gwamnati na kin sakin kusan fursunoni 600 Taliban da ta kira masu aikata manyan laifuka kuma ta ba su kyauta.
'Yan Taliban sun ki.
“Bangarorin sun fi kusa fiye da yadda za a fara tattaunawar tsakanin Afghanistan, muhimmin mataki na gaba na kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 40,” in ji sanarwar Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka.
“Kodayake an samu gagarumin ci gaba a kan musayar fursunoni, batun yana buƙatar ƙarin ƙoƙari don warware cikakkiyar matsala.”
Kakakin siyasar Taliban a farkon wannan makon yace a shirye yake ya gudanar da tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasar Kabul bayan hutun musulunci na Eid al-Adha a karshen watan nan, inda ya bada sanarwar an kammala sakin fursuna.
Babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shi ne kasancewa a Afghanistan na 'yan bindiga, musamman masu nasaba da TTP ko Jaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke tare da sojojin Liberation na Baluchistan, wanda ya dauki alhakin kai hare-haren sama a wannan watan a kudancin lardin Sindh da kuma kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan dake yaki da masu tayar da kayar baya.
TTP ta dauki alhakin daya daga cikin hare-haren muni da aka kai a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka kai wa wata makarantar sojojin Pakistan hari kuma an kashe 140.
Yawancin dalibai ne, wasu kuma sun kasance matasa ne kamar 5.
“Jimillar 'yan ta'addan Pakistan da ke kasashen waje a Afghanistan, da ke kawo barazana ga kasashen biyu, an kiyasta su a tsakanin 6,000 da 6,500, mafi yawansu suna da TTP,” in ji rahoton.
Babban bankin Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta “kafa tarko” don kamfanin Huawei na China a binciken Amurka - Labaran Kasuwanci na RT
Bankin London-headquartered Multinational Bank HSBC ya kai ga kafofin watsa labarun don a ce ba haka ba ne, kamar yadda kafofin watsa labarai na kasar Sin suka yi ikirarin, “kirkirar shaida” a kan Huawei, wanda ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kudi na kamfanin a Canada.
A wani sakon da ba a samu ba a yanzu a kan WeChat, mai bashi shawara ya ce ayyukansa ba su jawo binciken Amurka ba a cikin manyan masu samar da kayan sadarwa a duniya, kamar yadda binciken kamfanin Huawei ya yi kan zargin keta takunkumin Amurka a kan Iran ya fara sosai kafin shigowar bankin a karshen 2016.
“HSBC ba ta da wata damuwa ga Huawei kuma ba ta “frame” Huawei ba,” in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, inda ya kara da cewa ba zai taba gurbata wani gaskiya game da abokan huldarta ba.
“A martanin da Amurka DOJ ta [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka] ta bukaci bayani, Kungiyar HSBC kawai ta gabatar da hujjojin da suka dace.
HSBC bai “ƙirƙira” shaida ko “ɓoye” gaskiya ba.”
Har ila yau, a kan rt.com Birtaniya ta motsa don dakatar da Huawei daga cibiyar sadarwa ta 5G yana nuna manufofin Amurka na ƙasashen waje - George Galloway zuwa Boom Bust
An katange sakon a kan dandamali tare da bayanin cewa “ya karya dokoki” kuma ba a samuwa a yanzu.
Sanarwar ta zo ne jim kadan bayan kantunan watsa labarai na kasar Sin masu yawa, ciki har da jaridu masu nasaba da jihar, wadanda ake zargin HSBC na “kulla makirci” tare da Washington don kafa tarko ga
Kamfanin ya kasance a cikin rudanin diflomasiya fiye da shekara daya da rabi tun bayan da aka kama kamfanin Huawei CFO Meng Wanzhou a watan Disambar 2018 a Canada bisa tuhumarsa daga Amurka.
Meng na fuskantar zargin zamba domin zargin yin amfani da kamfanin harsashi don karya takunkumin da aka kakabawa Iran da kuma zargin kwance wa bankuna game da alakar da ke tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Skycom na Iran.
Bisa ga sabon shaidar da Global Times ta ambata, HSBC yana da masaniya game da dangantakar kamfanin Sin da Skycom.
Bankin ya yi adawa da “collude” tare da gwamnatin Amurka don tserewa hukunci mafi tsanani a 2012, lokacin da bankin ya shigar da karar kudi da takunkumin karya, ciki har da takunkumi akan Iran.
An umurce shi a lokacin da ya biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 a fansa da kuma hana duk wani kuskuren da aka kama.
“Shaidun sun nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantaka amma da gangan ta sayar da takardun kasuwancin abokin ciniki zuwa ga bangaren Amurka don gwamnatin Amurka ta iya kawar da mummunar dabi'ar bankin Birtaniya kuma ba ta hukunta shi ba a karkashin Yarjejeniyar Shari'ar 2012,” in ji jaridar a daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya shafi al'amarin.
A cikin wani gargadi da aka yi, jaridar mai kula da Beijing-ta kara da cewa mai bayar da bashi, idan aka tabbatar da shi da laifin wannan “collusion,” zai iya fuskantar “hukunci mai tsanani” a kasar Sin, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwanni na HSBC.
Wannan dai ba shi ne karo na farko da mashahurin bankin ya afka wuta a cikin 'yan makonnin nan ba.
A watan da ya gabata, an yi amfani da HSBC don tallafawa sabuwar dokar tsaro ta kasa ga Hong Kong, birnin da kasuwancinta ya fara kuma wanda ke asusun fiye da rabin ribar da ta samu.
Bankin ya fuskanci zargi daga bangarorin biyu - daga Yamma, tare da Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo yana kiran amincewa da “kamfani kowtow,” da kuma Gabas, tare da bangaren kasar Sin sun bada rahoton cewa an “belin shi.”
Masu kashe gobara sun sami ƙasa a jahar Lassen
Jami'an kashe gobara suna samun barna da wutar daji guda biyu da suka kone fiye da injin 30,000 a karamar hukumar Lassen, arewa maso gabashin Sacramento.
Wutar Zinari, wadda ta fara kudu da Adin, tana da kashi 40% dauke da ita yayin da take ci gaba da barazana ga gidaje da biri har ma da noma da dabbobi da ayyukan katako, jami'an Cal Fire sun ce a wani sabani da safiyar yau Asabar.
Bayan kone na tsawon kwanaki hudu, wutar ta kunno kai ta hanyar acan 21,000, ta lalata gidaje bakwai sannan ta tura ma'aikatan kashe gobara biyu zuwa asibiti.
Cikin dare, masu kashe gobara sunyi amfani da yanayi mai laushi don ginawa da ƙarfafa layin sarrafawa.
Amma ana sa ran iskar guguwa da karancin zafi ta hanyar Asabar.
Yammacin Susanville, karamin wuta da aka sani da Hog wutan ya lalata gine-gine biyu kuma ya cinye kimanin 10,000.
Wutar ta zauna cikin dare yayin da masu aikin kashe gobara suka yi aiki don yin maci da karfafa layukan sarrafawa, a cewar Ma'aikatar Kula da Gandun Daji da Kare Wuta.
Ya zuwa safiyar Asabar, kashi 45% ne ke dauke da kuma an kona shi na tsawon kwanaki shida.
A cikin zafin rana, tare da yanayin zafi sama da digiri 90 a yankin Susanville, alamomi masu laushi suna cikin hadarin haskakawa.
Yayinda ake barin wasu mazauna su koma gidajensu, wasu yankuna a duka yankunan wuta suna kasancewa a karkashin umarnin kwashe su.
Yan kunar bakin waken biyu da suka ji rauni a gobarar Zinari an sako su daga asibiti.
Aljeriya: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Algeria Loses a Patriot, Devised Militant, In ji Shugaba Teboune.
Algiers - Shugaban Jamhuriyar, Abdelmadjid Teboune, ya aike da sakon ta'aziyya ga mambobin jam'iyyar Peopl's National Assembly (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya rasu ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce Algeria “ta rasa wani dan kishin kasa kuma dan bindiga ya aikata sanadin mutanensa da al'ummarsa.”
Aljeriya ta yi hasarar yau, ta sanadiyar mutuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, dan kishin kasa kuma dan bindiga ne da ya aikata sanadin jama'arsa da al'ummarsa, mutumin da bai taba jurewa ba kuma wanda kudurinsa ya kasance cikakke tun daga lokacin da ya dauki makamai, tare da 'yan uwansa masu daraja Mujahedeen, har zuwa numfashinsa na karshe a kan wannan Bakin ciki ranar da za mu iya rusa kanmu kawai ga nufin Allah,” Shugaba Tebboune ya rubuta a sakonsa na ta'aziyya.
“Marigayi Mahmoud Guemama, zaman lafiya ya tabbata a gare shi, ya kasance wani ƙarni na musamman na 'yan kishin kasa da suka sadaukar da kansu don mahaifarsu,” ya kara da cewa shugaban Jamhuriyar.
“Marigayin ya sadaukar da rayuwarsa ga 'yantar da Aljeriya daga azabtar da mulkin mallaka, ta hanyar shiga sahun juyin juya hali a firimiya na rayuwa a 1960 a sansanin horarwa na Tahart na wilaya VI mai tarihi.”
“Marigayi Shugaban kasa sananne ne ga kowa saboda tabbatar da dan bindiga da kuma jajircewarsa wajen daura hoton wani mai wadata da kuma hada kai da Algeria,” in ji Shugaba Tebboune.
“A kudu mai nisa, marigayi Mahmoud Guemama yana jin dadin manyan sanannu a matsayin mai shiga tsakani, yana shiga tsakani don sulhunta 'yan'uwa a kasar baki daya a duk lokacin da wutar rikici ta kunno kai,” ya kara da cewa shugaban a sakon nasa.
“Duk waɗannan halaye da dabi'u sun sami marigayi Mahmoud Guemama da girmamawa da amincewar mutanen Tamanrasset waɗanda suka zaɓe shi ya wakilce su a cikin Ƙungiyar Jama'a ta Ƙasa (APN) saboda sharuɗɗa da dama, a lokacin da shi ne jakadan da kuma kare damuwar yankin da kuma burin sa mutane, har ma da wakili da kakakin dukkan 'yan Algeriya,” ya rubutawa shugaban kasar.
“Duk maganganun ta'aziyya ba za su isa su biya haraji ga mujahed Mahmoud Guemama ba, zaman lafiya ya tabbata a gare shi.
Yana barinmu ne a yau a lokacin da Algeria ke bukatarsa,” inji Shugaban.
“Ina addu'ar Allah Madaukaki Ya kewaye marigayin da rahamarSa Mai tsarki, Ya yi masa maraba a cikin aljannarSa mai fadi tare da shuhadaa da kyautatawa.
Ina kuma addu'ar Allah ya jikan iyalansa da masoyansa hakuri da nutsuwa... babu wani karfi ko iko sai a wajen Allah,” Shugaban kasar ya kammala.
Zanga-zangar Seattle: Gobarar wuta da Pepper Yaduwa Kamar Dubban Maris Ta Birnin
SEATTLD - Bayan makonni da aka yi na fuskantar rikici tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., taron mutane kimanin 2,000 sun tattara a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya ta tituna kuma suna rikici tare da 'yan sanda.
'Yan sanda uku sun samu raunuka, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar da shi a asibiti tare da rauni a kafa sanadiyyar wata fashewa, kuma an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 da sanyin safiyar jiya, in ji 'yan sandan.
Masu dauke da alamu kamar “Feds Go Home” da kuma ihu na “Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya,” masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya ne a shafin wata cibiyar tsare matasa da ke gaba da kuma haska gine-gine a can da wuta.
Wasu windows na kasuwancin da ke kusa.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci tarzoma a unguwar Capitol Hill, suna aikawa da gurneti masu haske da kuma fesa barkono kafin su fara daukar mutane a tsare.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, na Kirkland, Wash., ta ce ta yi zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce yana damuwa da ita ganin irin wannan mummunar dabara da 'yan sanda ke yi.
“Wannan ba ita ce kasar da na yi hijira zuwa ba,” in ji Misis Mukherjee, wacce ta isa daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka wuce.
“Yana jin kamar muna saurin zama yan jihar fasto da yan sandan jihar.”
Michaud Savage na Seattle yace masu zanga-zangar sun yi ne da nufin daukacin kananan hukumomi da kuma tura jami'an tarayya da suka yi tir da murkushe zanga-zangar da aka dade ana gudanarwa a Portland.
Mr. Savage ya ce hanyoyin tabbatar da doka a Portland, wadanda suka hada da amfani da iskar gas mai hawaye da kuma bindigogi masu sarrafa jama'a, sun kasance masu hadari kuma ba su dace ba.
“Yana da matukar wuya a cikin wani mummunan tashin hankali,” in ji Mista Savage yayin da ya wanke idanunsa na fesa barkono kuma ya yi jinya wani rauni a hannunsa daga wata gurnatin wuta.
Mutuwar George Floyd a tsare 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayu ta ƙone zanga-zangar lumana da ta jawo miliyoyi zuwa tituna a birane da dama, amma waɗannan zanga-zangar sun ɓace a mafi yawan birane.
Seattle da Portland, duk da haka, sun ga karin zanga-zanga.
Masu zanga-zangar Seattle a wani wuri sun dage suna da'awar tubalan da dama na unguwar Capitol Hill kuma sun ayyana yankin mai cin gashin kai.
Bayan jerin harbe-harbe a can ya sa 'yan sanda suka share yankin, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ta tallafa.
Portland, a halin yanzu, ta ci gaba da zanga-zanga, tare da wasu manyan zanga-zangar da ke kusa da gine-ginen tarayya a birnin.
Bayan Shugaba Trump ya ba da umarnin zartarwa don kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyar tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Gida ta tura ƙungiyoyi masu dabara zuwa birnin, fara jerin rikice-rikicen da suka haifar da raunuka masu zanga-zanga, bincike na musamman da kuma kira daga shugabannin gida don wakilan tarayya don barin.
Dandazon masu zanga-zanga a wannan birni sun kutsa cikin dubban, kuma ana ci gaba da zanga-zanga.
A wannan makon, jami'an tarayya sun tura wata tawagar dabara zuwa Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zangar sun caccaki wannan ci gaba a matsayin dalili daya na zanga-zangar ranar Asabar.
A yayin da masu zanga-zangar Portland suka yi gangami a cikin gari, zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar ta yi ta yawo yankunan da ke gabashin tsakiyar gari, inda gidan majalisar tarayya na birnin yake.
Virginia Beach ya sauka Confederate abin tunawa
Virginia Beach, Va. — Birnin Virginia Beach ya cire wani abin tunawa na Confederate mai shekaru 15 daga wuraren jama'a a ranar Asabar, kasa da kwanaki biyu bayan majalisar birnin ta kada kuri'ar amincewa da yin hakan.
Ma'aikata sun sauko da ƙafa 27 (8.2-mita) mai tsayi a ranar Asabar da safe, kantunan watsa labarai sun ruwaito.
An shigar da shi a 1905 kuma ya tsaya a wajen tsohuwar kotun Princess Anne County, a wuri guda da aka taba gudanar da auctions na bayi.
Majalisar ta jefa kuri'a baki daya Alhamis da dare domin fara aikin cire shi.
Majalisar ta saurari yawancin masu magana kuma ta yanke shawarar tunawa da mutane da yawa suna kallo a matsayin rarrabuwa da tunatarwa mai raɗaɗi na baya.
An rufe mutum-mutumin kwanan nan, tare da ƙofar kulle a kusa da shi bayan zanga-zangar da aka yi kwanan nan a wasu wuraren tarihi na Confederate.
Za a adana abin tunawa a yanzu.
Birnin yanzu dole ne ya jira duk wani tayin daga kungiyoyin tarihi ko wasu ƙungiyoyi da zasu so su dauki abin tunawa.
Kotun Masar ta nufi mutumin da ya kashe yara uku zuwa tantancewar kwakwalwa
Babban mai shari'ar Minya ta Kudu Tamer Motea ya yanke wa wani manomi hukuncin daurin kwanaki hudu a kurkuku a jiran bincike a kan dalilin da ya sa ya kashe 'ya'yansa uku yayin da kuma ya garzaya da shi ga wani kwamitin kula da kwakwalwa.
A ranar 24 ga watan Yuli ne Mohamed Ali mai shekaru 56 ya jefa 'ya'yansa Khadiga, hudu, Mena, takwas, da Omar, shida, a gaban wani jirgin kasa mai motsi a Tashar Jirgin Kasa ta Malawi.
An samu Ali yana babbaka ba bisa ka'ida ba a yayin bincike, inda ya kai ga zargin yana fama da tabin hankali.
Matarsa ta karyata ta sha fama da wata matsala tare da shi kuma ta danganta halayyarsa ga al'amuran da suka shafi kwakwalwa.
Mazauna kauyuka daga Massart Mallawi sun ƙi yin magana game da lamarin, suna ba da ta'aziyyarsu kawai ga iyalan yara.
Kusan kashi 93 cikin 100 na yaran Masar masu shekaru daya zuwa 14 suna fama da tashin hankali, inji Khalid Darwish, mai ba da shawara ga hukumar kula da kananan yara da mahaifa baya a watan Oktoba.
Shari'ar yana daya daga cikin ginshikai masu muhimmanci wajen kawar da cin zarafin yara, ya kara da cewa, yana mai jaddada muhimmancin hadin kai tsakanin majalisa da kuma hukunta jama'a a wannan fanni.
Bisa ga wani bincike da hukumar kula da yara da mahaifa ta kasa ta shirya, yara na fuskantar tashin hankali a wuraren da ya kamata su zama lafiya, kamar gida, makaranta ko kulki, da kuma fallasa tarzoma daga mutanen da ya kamata su kula da su, kamar iyaye ko malamai.
Kwadago anti-Semitism whistleblowers bukatar Corbyn a fitar ko fuskantar karar
