Magoya bayan Mr Corbyn sun ce Mr Starmer yana bukatar mayar da hankali a kan magance matsalolin da ake gudanarwa a kan coronavirus maimakon komawa cikin sassan cikin gida.
Wata majiya mai suna tsohon dan kwadago ta fadawa Daily Mail cewa za su dauki matakin shari'a ko da Mr Starmer ya yi fito-na-fito da Mr Corbyn.
“Ina nufin da gaske yake, ya sanya jam'iyyar Labour ta sake tsayawa takara.”
