Tauraron dutsen ya rubuta kusa da shi da matarsa Anita Dobson: “Abincin abincin dare a gare ni - wanda Anita ya halitta - mun yi ado don zama gida!”
Sakataren gida Priti Patel ya bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a kan 'abhorrent' Wiley tweets
Priti Patel ya bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a tsawon lokacin da ya dauka don cire “abhorrent” da Wiley ya yi.
Yanzu haka 'yan sanda suna binciken jerin maganganun antisemitic da aka fitar a asusun sada zumunta na Grime.
Sakataren cikin gida ya tweeted a ranar Lahadi: “Abubuwan da ke cikin antisemitic daga Wiley suna da ban tsoro.”
“Bai kamata su samu damar kasancewa a Twitter da Instagram ba har tsawon lokaci kuma na tambaye su cikakken bayani.”
“Dole ne kamfanonin kafofin watsa labarun suyi aiki da sauri don cire irin wannan ƙiyayya mai ƙiyayya daga dandamali.”
An zargi Twitter da “watsi da antisemitism” kamar yadda tweets Wiley ta kasance har yanzu bayyane 12 hours bayan da aka fara buga su.
Yawancin tweets tun lokacin da aka cire kuma an ba da izinin 41 mai shekaru bakwai ta shafin.
Twitter a baya ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na dan lokaci “don keta manufofin halayyar mu,” yayin da Facebook ya ce babu “babu wani wuri don maganganun ƙiyayya a Instagram.”
'Yan Sandan Metropolitan sun ce a ranar Asabar: “Met yana daukan dukkan rahotanni na antisemitism da gaske. Ana tantance abubuwan da suka dace.”
A halin yanzu, kamfanin gudanarwa na Wiley, A-List Management, “yanke dukkan dangantaka” tare da tauraron.
A yanzu tsohon manajan wasan kwaikwayo, John Woolf, wanda yake Yahudawa, ya rubuta a Twitter: “Bin Wiley na antisemitic tweets a yau mu a @A_ListMGMT sun yanke duk dangantaka da shi. Babu wani wuri a cikin al'umma domin antisemitism.”
Ya yi a baya ya ce bai goyi bayan ko ya yi ta'aziyya da abin da Wiley ya wallafa ba amma zai yi magana da shi a sirrance kuma ya “taimaka wajen ilmantar da shi.”
Duk da haka, a wani bidiyo a Instagram, Wiley ya bayyana cewar shi ne wanda ya yanke dangantaka da gudanarwar sa.
Sauran MPs sun soki Twitter don barin tweets su kasance a bayyane.
MP na kwadago Jess Phillips ya ce a ranar Asabar:
“Kawai ka ga duk kayan Wiley ne. Me ya sa a duniya suka @Twitter ya bar irin wannan antisemitism da ƙiyayya? Ya fadi duk hatsari mai haɗari, Yahudawa suna samun abubuwan da ba ku samu ba, suna cikin iko, suna ganin mafi kyau... Wannan abu ne mai haɗari. Lalle ne shi ya sauka.”
Fellow MP Neil Coyle ya kara da cewa: “Gudanarwar sa ta bayyana iya yin aiki da sauri fiye da @Twitter da ya jaddada, sake cewa doka (ciki har da Bill Harms) ya kamata a tabbatar da ba a yi amfani da dandalin kafofin watsa labarun don yada ƙiyayya ba.”
John Mann, mai ba da shawara na gwamnati mai zaman kanta a kan antisemitism, ya ce tweets “sun nuna ainihin dalilin da ya sa doka ke buƙatar canzawa don rike su zuwa asusun da ya dace.”
A halin yanzu, Campaign Antisemitism ya bukaci 'yan sanda su bincika abubuwan da Wiley ya yi kuma ya yi kira ga asusun kafofin watsa labarun da za a rufe “don hana karin fitar da kwayar cutar Yahudawa.”
Wiley, wanda aka fi sani da Godfather na Grime kuma wanda ainihin sunansa Richard Cowie, ya karbi MBE don ayyuka don kiɗa a 2018.
Amurka “kasawa” suna riƙe da binciken magunguna na coronavirus
Kokarin da duniya ke yi na samar da magunguna masu amfani da covid ke hankoron Amurka saboda masu bincike suna gwada kwayoyi a “hanyar da ba ta dace ba, mai son zuciya,” masanin da ke jagorantar shirin Birtaniya ya yi gargadin.
Shirin gwajin farfadowa da Birtaniya, wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitocin Birtaniya ɗari, ya riga ya nuna alamar sabon magani don magance cutar kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - a baya ana tunanin su zama masu ceton rai - a matsayin marasa amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin kiwon lafiya na Amurka don daidaita wannan fitarwa yana nufin cewa sauran jiyya masu ban sha'awa da za a iya kawar da su don yin amfani da tartsatsi har yanzu za a kimanta.
Musamman ma, ƙwayar jini (jini wanda aka ɗauka daga marasa lafiya na Covid-19 kuma wanda ya ƙunshi magungunan da za su iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu za a gwada su sosai a kan gwaji mai girma.
“An riga an bai wa dubban mutane kwayoyin cutar sankara a Amurka amma wadannan jiyya ba su yi karo da su ba,” in ji Farfesa Martin Landray, daya daga cikin wadanda suka kafa shirin farfadowa da farfadowa.
“Kawai suna ba mutane kwarai da jini a cikin bege zai yi aiki. An bayar da dimbin yawa kuma har yanzu ba su da masaniyar ko yana taimakawa ko harbin ko ba shi da wani tasiri,” ya kara da cewa Landray, wani kwararre a wajen kafa gwajin magunguna masu dimbin yawa.
US ne kasawa ya yi manyan, da ka gwaji da kuma cewa ya ƙare har samar da miyagun magani.
Gwajin miyagun ƙwayoyi da aka yi da su sune daidaitattun zinariya don yin amfani da magunguna masu amfani.
Suna cire rashin sani biases cewa zai girgije clinicians 'hukunce-hukuncen.
Dubban mutane ne aka ba su magani kuma dubban wasu ana ba su wani placebo.
Babu wanda ya san ko wanne ne aka ba su.
Sa'an nan kuma an kwatanta sakamakon da kuma ingancin maganin da aka bayyana.
Ta wannan hanyar, farfadowa ya iya nuna cewa steroid dexamethasone rage mutuwar da na uku a Covid-19 marasa lafiya a kan ventilators.
Har ila yau, ya nuna cewa magungunan hydroxychloroquine - da kuma haɗuwa da maganin lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da wani tasiri a ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Giccially wadannan gwaje-gwajen bukatar sosai yawan marasa lafiya da kuma babu daya asibiti da ya isa ga irin wannan bincike.
Britaniya tana da amfani guda ɗaya - sabis na kiwon lafiya na kasa.
Ta bambanta, sabis na kiwon lafiya na Amurka ya ragu kuma nasarar da ta samu kawai wajen nuna yiwuwar magani ya nuna amfani da magungunan da ke da tsada sosai don sake dawo da wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
“Akwai kuri'a da magungunan kananan kwayoyi da suka hada da wasu 'yan dozin ko 'yan dari da ke faruwa a Amurka amma babu wani abu,” in ji Landray.
“Suna kasawa su yi manyan, da ka gwaji da kuma cewa ya ƙare har samar da miyagun magani. Yana sa aikin magani ya talauce kuma sakamakon ga marasa lafiya ya talauce.”
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar ta yi matukar tayar da hankali a lokacin da ya yi amfani da kwayar cutar sankara, wadda likitoci da dama suka yi imanin za su iya samun muhimmiyar rawa da za su taka wajen magance rashin lafiya mai tsanani Covid-19.
“Idan ka dubi Amurka, an yi amfani da yawa na wannan magani a kan wani m son zuciya. Birtaniya ta yi fice fiye da ma'auni idan aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can,” ya kara da cewa.
Farfesa Peter Horby, kwararre kan cututtuka masu yaduwa da kuma sauran wanda ya kafa shirin farfadowa, ya ce: “Akwai rahotanni game da marasa lafiya 20,000 da ke samun plasma a cikin mahaifa amma babu wani daga cikin wadanda marasa lafiya da aka yi da su.
Idan sun sanya wadannan marasa lafiya cikin gwaje-gwajen da aka yi, yanzu za mu sami amsa mai kyau game da tasirin kwayar cutar.”
Horby ya kara da cewa yanzu farfadowa da Birtaniya ta kaddamar da gwajin da aka yi na rikitarwa na plasma amma ba ya tsammanin sakamakon zai kasance a shirye sai daga bisani a wannan shekarar.
Masar ta fara yin rajistar bayanai na masu jefa kuri'a a kasashen waje don zaben majalisar dattawa
Hukumar gudanar da zaben kasa (NEA) a ranar Asabar ta fara yin rijistar bayanan masu kada kuri'a a sama domin fara jefa kuri'unsu a zaben majalisar dattijai da za a gudanar a ranakun 9 da 10 ga watan Agusta, a cewar shafin intanet na NEA.
Dole ne masu kada kuri'a su yi rajistar bayanan su da kuma aikin diflomasiyya da ke da alaka da gidansu a kasashen waje a shafin yanar gizon NEA daga ranar 25 ga watan Yuli har zuwa
Har ila yau, hukumar ta NEA ta wallafa wani bidiyo da ke bayyana matakan da masu jefa kuri'a za su iya dauka don jefa kuri'unsu da kyau ta hanyar imel, a matsayin wani ɓangare na kariya daga cututtukan coronavirus.
Lokacin shari'a na dan takarar sanata zabe Farfesan ya gudana ne daga ranar 26 ga watan Yuli har zuwa ranar 8 ga watan Agusta, inji NAN.
Ministan Harkokin Hijira da Harkokin Waje na Masar Nabila Makram ya yi kira ga masu jefa kuri'a Masar a kasashen waje da su shiga zaben kamar yadda kundin tsarin mulkin su ya tanada.
Majalisar Wakilai ta Masar a ranar 17 ga watan Yuni ta amince da dokar kafa majalisar dattijai, wadda za ta yi aiki a matsayin gidan sama na majalisar dokoki.
