Wa'adin zama mamba a majalisar dattijai zai zama shekaru biyar, farawa daga ranar da aka fara taronta.
Za a zabi sabon taron ne a cikin kwanaki sittin kafin karshen wa'adinsa.
'Yan sanda suna gwada sababbin kayan aiki, ƙananan mutuwa yayin da zanga-zangar ke ci gaba
Yayin da rikice-rikicen tashin hankali ke ci gaba tsakanin tilasta doka da masu zanga-zanga a Portland da kewayen kasar, muhawara tana juyawa game da yadda 'yan sanda za su iya yanke baya a kan karfi mai mutuwa.
Wasu kamfanoni suna haɓaka don samar da sababbin kayan aiki na fasaha kamar kayan aiki na nesa don 'yan sanda su yi amfani da su maimakon zaɓuɓɓuka masu haɗari kamar feshin barkono, harsasai na roba da gurneti.
Kungiyar kare hakkin bil'adama ta Amnesty International ta bincikar bidiyon 500 daga zanga-zangar daga ranar 26 ga watan Mayu zuwa Yuni 5 kuma ta sami abubuwan 125 na matsanancin karfi a fadin jihohi 40 da gundumar Columbia.
“Mun ga rashin amfani da iskar gas, barkono barkono, barkono bukukuwa, 40 millimeter tasiri zagaye, m kowane hade da makamin da aka yi amfani da shi ta hanyoyin da ba su dace ba,” in ji mai binciken makamai na Amnesty International Brian Castner.
Duk da haka, wasu sun nace cewa samun zaɓuɓɓuka yana da mahimmanci don kauce wa buƙatar wuta.
“Duk wadannan na'urori ya kamata su kasance a hannun 'yan sanda su yi amfani da banda karfi na jiki da ake amfani da shi ta hanyar kashe wuta saboda kawai sana'a ce a Amurka inda 'yan kasar ke ba ka damar tafiyar da rayuwarka,” in ji Corey Pegues, tsohon mataimakin sufeton 'yan sanda na New York.
Ɗaya daga cikin sababbin kayan aikin shine ake kira Bola Wrap, na'urar da aka yi da hannu wanda ke harbe wani igiyar Kevlar mai kafa 8 wanda ke kunshe a kusa da wani abin da ake zargi.
Akwai Long Range Acoustic Devices, wanda aka fi sani da sound canons, makaman makamashi masu amfani da lasers don dumama fatar mutum, sababbin kayan da aka yi daga abubuwa kamar kumfa da alli, bama-bamai, kuma ba shakka Taser.
Hannun jari na Axon, kamfanin da ke sa Taser, ya yi sama da 18%, yana kai duk lokacin da masu zanga-zangar suka juya kwanakin tashin hankali bayan 'yan sanda sun kashe George Floyd.
Ana sa ran kasuwar kera makamai masu karanci za ta kai dala biliyan 11.85 nan da shekarar 2023.
Dubi bidiyon don kallon sabon kayan aikin fasaha na 'yan sanda suna amfani da su don ƙarancin ƙarfi, yadda aka tsara su, da kuma abin da ke cikin gungumen azaba don makomar 'yan sanda da al'ummomin da suke aiki.
Magajin garin Kansas yana maraba da taimakon tarayya wajen magance kisan kai, amma damuwa game da dalilan Trump
Magajin garin birnin Kansas Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi shugaba Trump kan dalilan tura wakilan tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon wajen warware matsalar kashe kashen da ake yi a birnin Midyammacin kasar, yana tunanin matsa zai iya zama karin game da buoying damar sake zaben Trump.
“Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon [cewa] shugaban kasar ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci motsin Black Lives Matter,” Lucas, wani dan Democrat, ya ce a “Fox News Sunday” na zanga-zangar da aka yi kwanan nan a kan rashin daidaito launin fata da kuma cin zarafin 'yan sanda.
“Ba haka lamarin yake ba a Birnin Kansas. Mun samu ƙaruwar shekara-da-shekara [amma] abin da muke buƙatar taimako a kan shi ne ainihin share wasu daga cikin kisan da ba a warware ba.”
Lucas ya kara da cewa: “Bari mu yi ƙoƙari mu yi ƙoƙari mu mayar da hankali ga magance kisan kai... Ina tsammanin idan kun saurari maganganun da aka yi kwanan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da wakilan tarayya a cikin iyakacin iyaka.”
Duk da shirye-shiryensa na samun wakilan tarayya suna aiki tare da aiwatar da doka na gida, Lucas ya ce maganganun Trump - musamman dangane da rikice-rikicen da ke kewaye da dabarar da aka yi aiki a Portland, Ore., daga wakilan tarayya - ya sa da yawa daga cikin mazabarsa suka nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'ai a kan titunan birni.
“Abin da ba mu bukata shi ne karin man fetur a kan wuta daga wakilan tarayya su yi, ina ganin, wani al'amarin siyasa mai ban sha'awa,” in ji shi.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura wakilan tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance tashin wasu laifuffuka - matsin da ke nuna fadada bakin hauren fadar White House zuwa cikin dokar cikin gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin “doka da oda” shugaban kasa.
“surutai” na jami'ai da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka na daga cikin Operation Legend - mai suna bayan Legend Taliferro mai shekaru 4, wanda aka harbe shi matuka yayin da yake barci a wani gidan birnin Kansas a karshen watan jiya.
Yayin tura wakilan tarayya don taimakon doka ta gida ba a taɓa gani ba - Babban Lauya Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunkuri a watan Disamba don birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin wakili na tarayya da ake aikawa, da kuma wasu dabarunsu, sun tayar da damuwa a tsakanin jihohi da na gida masu shari'an.
Wasu lauyoyi da dama daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi furuci kan gwamnatin Trump da ke tura jami'ai zuwa garuruwansu, musamman biyo bayan rahotannin cewa jami'an tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun dauke su a cikin motocin da ba a san su ba.
An buga Portland da zanga-zanga ta yau da kullum game da cin zarafin 'yan sanda da tsarin wariyar launin fata tun mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake tsare 'yan sandan Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
Ƙananan hukumomi sun yi korafin cewa hawan ya tsananta tashin hankali ne kawai, kuma masana shari'a na aikata laifuka sun ce ƙoƙari ya yi bayani saboda lokacin da ba a taɓa gani ba Amurka tana rayuwa - tare da annoba, rashin aikin tarihi da kuma la'akari da wariyar launin fata da kuma yadda mutane masu launi suke bi da 'yan sanda.
AP blasts White House Press sakataren labarai Kayleigh McEnany don “siyasa” taƙaitaccen bayani - amma masu rahoto suna riƙe da tambayoyin siyasa - RT Amurka News
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakataren yada labarai na White House Kayleigh McEnDuk da damuwa da kafofin watsa labarai ta hanyar yi mata bayani game da siyasa maimakon bayani - a bayyane yake manta cewa masu rahoto sun zabi tambayoyin.
Wani labarin ranar Asabar da AP, mafi girma kamfanin dillancin labarai na Amurka, ya ce bayanin labaran White House na iya zama “karya al'adar,” kamar yadda Mcenany ya sanya su “wani tsari, mai cikakkiyar talla ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zaben, wani wuri don kai hare-hare a kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da ya fi haske a kan bayani” game da abin da gwamnati take yi.
Ƙarshe na waɗannan tabbatarwa ba shi da tabbas, kamar yadda da wuya an bayyana wani sabon bayani a taƙaitaccen bayani.
Abin da AP ya kasa ambata shi ne cewa da wuya an nemi wani sabon bayani a zahiri a cikin taƙaitaccen bayani.
Masu bayar da rahoto akai-akai suna amfani da 'yan jarida na White House don jawo hankalin kansu, wani nau'i na fasaha wanda Jim Acosta ya kammala.
Sun wuce dangantaka ta kafofin watsa labarai, suna maimaita juna wajen yin tambayoyin gotcha da nufin kawai don tabbatar da shugaba Donald Trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna sa kansu labarai, kamar lokacin da CBS News mai ba da rahoto Weijia Jiang ya mayar da martani ga wani “tambayi China” ya karɓa daga Trump ta hanyar yin wata alama mai mahimmanci a wariyar launin fata: “Sir, me ya sa kake cewa a gare ni musamman?”
A Yuli 6 briefing bayar da wani firayim misali na cire haɗin kan yadda bayanai suka daina zama tushen bayani mai ma'ana ga Amurkawa.
Trump ya tweeted waccan safiya cewa hotunan gidan talabijin na NASCAR sun ciwo ta ne bisa zargin karya da ake yi masa na laifin kiyayya kan direba Bubba Wallace da kuma hukuncinsa na dakatar da nuna tutar Confederate a abubuwan da suka faru.
Abin takaici, mafi yawan tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet kamar yadda mai ba da rahoto ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyi da aka tsara don ya sa ta ce Trump yana goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
McEnany bai samar da masu ba da amsa da ake so ba - wani sauti mai sauti wanda zai cutar da Trump - amma ta mayar da martani akai-akai ta hanyar cewa shugaban ba ya daukar matsayi a kan tutar Confederate kuma cewa gist na sakonsa shi ne cewa magoya bayan NASCAR suna nuna ba daidai ba a matsayin wariyar launin fata.
AP ta ce ta yi wakar “exaspered” a lokacin da take jawabi.
Labarin AP ya nuna wani shafi na Washington Post a baya a wannan watan wanda kamfanin labarai na ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shi ne shugaban kungiyar White House Confidents Association.
Karl ya jaddada cewa, “karyata gaskiya da yin amfani da fadar White House don dalilai na siyasa zalla cin zarafin jama'a ne.”
Amma duk da haka McEnany ta saurin wit da salon hada baki sun sanya ta zama gwarzon wasu magoya bayan Trump, tun bayan da ta bayar da jawabinta na farko a ranar 1 ga watan Mayu bayan shan kaye a matsayin sakataren manema labarai a watan Afrilu.
'Yan matsa sun bazu fiye da shekara guda kafin a nada ta.
Kamar sauran fannoni na rayuwar siyasa a Washington, sakataren yada labarai na White House ya canzawa matuka a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canjin ya fito ne daga bangarorin biyu kuma tun kafin zuwan McEnany.
Wani gishiri na tsohon sakataren watsa labarai Sarah kabee Sanders da mai wasan barkwanci Michelle Wolf a White House Consulents” abincin dare a watan Afrilu 2018 ya kasance mummunan cewa har ma MSNBC ya karbi bakuncin Mika Brzezinski ya kira shi “deplorable.”
Mai ba da rahoto na AP White House Jill Colvin ya gaishe da McEnany a jawabinta na farko ta hanyar tambayar, “Shin za ku jingina ba za ku taba karya mana daga wannan filin ba?”
Mai nazarin harkokin siyasa na Fox News Brit Hume, tsohon soja mai shekaru fiye da 50 a aikin jarida wanda ke da shekaru 1989-1996 a matsayin mai ba da labari na ABC ta White House, ya ce masu gabatar da labarai a yau suna nuna “mummunan hali” a cikin dakin jawabin saboda irin kwarewarsu ga Trump.
Saboda abinda suka hana Trump mayar da hankali, in ji shi a wannan makon a kan shirin Fox na Tucker Carlson Tuthday, 'yan jarida suna sakaci wajen tara labarai na manufofi.
“Ba wasa ne kawai na gotcha ba,” Hume ya ce daga cikin manufar da aka nufa da 'yan matsa.
“Ba kawai wani yunkuri ne na kunyata wani jami'in gwamnati ba. Shine ya tsantsa bayani.”
