Babban jami'in Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya tsallake ziyarar Pakistan, yana fitar da batun jirgin
ISLABAD (AP) - Shugaban mai shigowa zauren majalisar dinkin duniya ya sanar Lahadi cewa ya jinkirta ziyarar da aka shirya yi zuwa Pakistan “saboda wasu matsalolin jiragen fasaha.”
An zabi jami'in diflomasiyar Turkiya Volkan Bozkir shugaban rikon kwaryar 75 na babban zauren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a watan jiya kuma an shirya zai isa Islamabad a ranar Lahadi.
Amma a wani sakon Twitter, yace ziyarar da zai kai babban birnin Pakistan zata jira.
Ministan waje na Pakistan Shah Mahmood Qureshi ya mayar da martani ga Bozkir cewa “Ina sa ido in yi muku maraba da zuwa Pakistan nan ba da dadewa ba domin ziyarar mai kayatarwa da ban haushi.”
Kwana guda da ya gabata, wani mai suna Qureshi, yayin sanar da ziyarar, ya yi fatan zai tattauna kan batutuwan da suka shafi Bozkir, ciki har da Kashmir, wanda aka raba tsakanin Pakistan da makwabtan India da kuma ikirarin duka a gabanta.
Pakistan da Indiya sun yi yaki biyu daga cikin yake-yakensu uku kan yankin da ake jayayya tun samun 'yancin kai daga mulkin Birtaniya a shekarar 1947.
Bangarorin biyu sukan yi musayar wuta a Kashmir, abinda ya haddasa dakaru da fararen hula a garesu.
Pakistan tana son Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta taka rawa wajen warware batun Kashmir karkashin kudurinta ta barin mutanen da ke zaune a yankin Himalayan su yanke shawarar ko suna son hadewa da Indiya, da Pakistan ko kuma sun fi son 'yancin kai.
'Me ya faru a can?! '
UFC fighter Correia yana samun damuwa bayan ya juya baya a kan kishiya kuskuren tunanin zagaye ya wuce (bidiyo) - Labarun wasanni na RT
Bantamweight na Brazil Betheat Correia tsohon dan wasan UFC ne amma ya yi wani mai son kuskure ta hanyar juya baya akan abokin hamayyarsa Pannie Kianzad da kuskuren tunanin zagaye ya wuce a fafatawarsu a tsibirin Fight, kuma ya samu tagomashi sakamakon haka.
Kawo karshen zangon farko na stanza da suka nuna a undcard a Abu Dhabi, Correia mai shekaru 37 ta bayyana kuskuren gargadi na 10 ga ainihin karshen zagaye, inda ta kai ga fitar da wata safar kafin ta juya bayanta kan Kianzad tare da mayar mata da hanyarta zuwa kwanciyarta.
Jirgin saman Sweden ya yi fice ba tare da jinkiri ba, yana ɗaukar abokin hamayyarsa da hannun dama kafin ya bi tare da jerin ƙuƙwalwa don mayar da Correia a kan cage.
Wani lokaci da yake fitowa a cikin haɗari, Brazil sai ta sake samun iko don tsuke barazanar da kuma mayar da Kianzad kafin a kira ainihin ƙarshen zagaye.
“Me ya faru a wurin? Oh maganata,” an ji tawagar sharhin akan ESPN+ suna furtawa.
Shi ne kawai wani ɓangare na wani abin takaici dare ga tsohon bantamweight title mai kalubalantar Correia, wanda ya sauka zuwa daya yanke shawara shan kashi wanda shi ne ta uku asara a baya hudu octagon fitarwa kuma ya bar ta overall rikodin a 11-5, tare da daya zana.
Ga Iraniya-haifaffen Kianzad, 28, shi ne nasara ta biyu a kan juyawa bayan nasarar da ta samu a kan Jessica-Rose Clark a UFC Fight Night a Moscow a watan Nuwamba.
Kianzad yanzu yana 13-5 gaba daya da 2-1 a UFC, kamar yadda matar da aka fi sani da 'Banzai' ke nufin matsawa har da martabar 135lbs.
A wasu wurare a cikin dare, Robert Whittaker na Australia ya fitar da Darren Till na Ingila a cikin babban taron, yayin da mawakin da aka haifa na Rasha Khamzat Chimaev ya yi tarihi ta hanyar lashe wani karo na biyu a cikin kwanaki 10 a kan tsibirin Fight, mafi karancin lokaci tsakanin nasarori a zamanin UFC.
