Jamie Vardy ya bayyana jin dadinsa a bace a wasan kwallon kafa na Champions League, amma yace Leicester City sun cimma burinsu na farko na cancantar zuwa Turai.
Foxes sun kasance na biyu a watan Disamba da na uku lokacin da kwallon kafa ta sake dawowa bayan kulle, amma sun dauki maki hudu kacal daga wasanninsu biyar na karshe a kammala na biyar a gasar Premier.
A wasan daf da na karshe kan Manchester United za ta kulla karawar sama-da-hudu, amma bangaren Brendan Rodgers ya sha fama da asarar 2-0, wanda Vardy yace shi ne al'amari mafi tayar da hankali.
“Abin takaici ne, mafi yawan hanyar da muka ƙare har muka rasa wasan,” in ji shi a kan Sky Sports a cikakken lokaci.
“Amma mun ce a cikin dakin kwalliya, mun yi niyya a bayan kofofin da aka rufe don cancantar zuwa Turai kuma mun yi hakan.”
“Mun samu damar cancantar zuwa gasar zakarun Turai kuma hakan ya fi kyau, amma za mu yi tunani a kai kuma mu dawo da karfi a shekara mai zuwa.”
“Yana da wuyar ɗauka, amma babban manufarmu ita ce Turai kuma mun gudanar da hakan.”
Yayin da kungiyarsa ta fadi takaicin, Vardy da kansa ya kare kakar wasa ta bana a matsayin babban dan wasan Premier League mai shekaru 33, kunnen doki sau 23.
Ya biya haraji ga abokan takararsa wajen karɓar kyautar kuma ya ce har yanzu akwai yalwar mil da suka rage a cikin shi a saman matakin, duk da shekarun da ya ci gaba.
“Nayi farin ciki, komai game da kungiyar. Ba zan kasance a matsayin da nake don burin ba tare da su ba kuma na sanya 'yan kadan.”
“Zan sami hutawa don dan kadan yanzu kuma in dawo don kakar wasa ta gaba. Abin farin ciki bana jin shekaruna, kafafuna suna nan lafiya kuma taba itace ban tsinci raunuka da yawa ba, don haka yana gab da ajiye a saman hakan kuma ya dawo da karfi kamar yadda zan iya shekara mai zuwa.”
Coronavirus: Matafiya daga Spain sun fada wa kwata-kwata
Matafiya da suka isa Birtaniya daga Spain dole ne yanzu su yi kwata-kwata don kwanaki 14, a karkashin sababbin dokokin tafiya na coronavirus.
An sanar da su ne a ranar Asabar biyo bayan barkewar cutar coronavirus a kasar Spain, tare da sabbin kamu da cutar fiye da 900 da aka ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
Jami'an Spain sun kuma yi gargadin guguwar ta biyu za ta iya kasancewa mai nisan zango kamar yadda manyan biranen kasar suka ga lamarin ya rutsa
Kamfanonin jiragen sama da suka hada da British Airways sun soki sabbin matakan a matsayin “duk da haka wani busa” ga masu hutu na Birtaniya.
Mutanen da a halin yanzu suke hutu a Spain sun shawarci Ma'aikatar Sufuri da su bi dokokin gida, su koma gida kamar yadda aka saba, kuma su duba shafin yanar gizon shawara na ofishin waje don ƙarin bayani.
Ofishin Harkokin Waje yana ba da shawara game da duka amma muhimmin tafiya zuwa yankin Spain, duk da haka matakan da aka samu sun shafi wadanda suka dawo daga yankin Spain, tsibirin Canary da tsibiran Balearic, kamar Majorca da Ibiza.
Shawarar Ofishin Harkokin Waje yana da ramifications don inshora na tafiya.
Daga cikin wadanda sabbin dokokin ya shafa akwai Sakatare Grant Shapps, wanda ya fara hutunsa a Spain ranar Asabar.
Ana sa ran zai ci gaba da tafiyarsa kamar yadda aka tsara kuma ya ware bisa layi da shiriya a kan dawowarsa.
An fara gabatar da matakan kwata-kwata ga matafiya na Birtaniya a farkon watan Yuni.
Amma bayan matsin lamba daga kamfanonin jiragen sama da na tafiye-tafiye, gwamnati da hukumomin gwamnati sun wallafa jerin ƙasashe ba su da izini.
Kamfanin jiragen sama na British Airways ya ce yana “jin kunya” game da sauye-sauyen da gwamnati ta yi kan shawarar tafiya da dokoki, kodayake kamfanin jiragen ya ce jiragensa suna ci gaba da aiki.
Ya ce motsi shi ne “jefa dubban shirye-shiryen tafiya na Britaniya cikin hargitsi.”
Kungiyar masu kula da filayen jiragen sama ta ce sabbin matakan za su “kara lalata abin da ya riga ya zama maras tushe a bangaren sufurin jiragen sama wanda ke ci gaba da fuskantar kalubale mafi girma a tarihinsa.”
Babbar katafariyar harkokin yawon bude ido ta Birtaniya, Tue, ta soke jiragenta saboda ficewa zuwa babban birnin Spain da tsibiran Canary a ranar Lahadi.
Abokan ciniki a halin yanzu suna hutu za su iya dawowa kan jirgin da suka nufa gida.
Duk da haka, kamfanin jiragen sama na kasafin kuɗi EasyJet ya ce yana “jin kunya” kuma zai yi aiki da cikakken tsari a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
“Abokan ciniki da ba sa son tafiya za su iya tura jiragensu ba tare da kudin canji ba ko kuma karbar takardar shaidar darajar wurin,” in ji kamfanin a cikin wata sanarwa.
Wani mai magana da yawun kungiyar British Travel Agents (Abta) ya ce canjin mulkin gwamnati kwata-kwata ya kasance “abin takaici.”
“Muna ba da shawarar gwamnati ta ɗauki dokoki na kwata-kwata don jirage zuwa da kuma daga wasu yankuna da ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta, ko zuwa wurare kamar Balearic Islands ko Canaries - waɗanda suke da bambanci daga yankin Spain - don kauce wa ƙarin lalacewar Birtaniya da kuma fita yawon shakatawa masana'antu,” inji shi.
Spain ya zuwa yanzu ta ga fiye da mutuwar coronavirus 28,000.
A ranar Alhamis, ya ga babbar yawaitar cututtukan yau da kullum tun lokacin da kulle shi ya kare.
Catalonia ya zama sabon yanki don ƙuƙwalwa a kan rayuwar dare.
Yankin arewa maso gabas mai arziki, wanda yake gida ga Barcelona, ya umarci dukan 'yan wasan dare su rufe na makonni biyu kuma su sanya tsakar dare a kan mashaya a yankin Barcelona mafi girma.
Hedikwatar BBC ta Guy Hedgecoe da ke Madrid ta ce cudanya tsakanin matasa abin damuwa ne, kamar yadda ake taruwa a manyan lambobi a birane da dare.
Faransa ta gargadi 'yan kasarta kada su yi balaguro zuwa Catalonia yayin da Norway ta ce za ta fara kwata-kwata mutanen da suka isa daga Spain.
Gwamnatin tana rokon ma'aikata su kasance “fahimtar wadanda suka dawo daga Spain wadanda yanzu za su bukaci su ware kansu.”
Amma inuwar gida sakataren kwadago Nick Thomas-Symonds ya yi kira ga gwamnati da ta yi bayani dalla-dalla kan yadda za ta tallafa wa wadanda abin ya shafa, inda ya kara da cewa labarai za su kasance “abin takaici ne ga iyalan da suke cikin kama a Spain ko kuma suna shirin tafiya.”
First ministan Scottish Nicola Sturgeon tweeted ya ce an yanke shawarar ne bayan yin nazari kan sabbin bayanai da suka gabata a ranar Asabar.
“Wannan yana ƙarfafa batun cewa waɗannan al'amura suna iya canzawa a taƙaice sanarwa don haka shawarata ita ce a yi taka tsantsan game da tafiye-tafiye na kasashen waje da ba su da muhimmanci,” in ji ta.
John Blackmore, daga Hampshire, ya kasance saboda tashi daga iyalinsa a Spain tare da matarsa da yara kanana biyu.
Amma sabbin dokokin na nufin sai ya soke, don fargabar matarsa mai aiki ba zai samu damar saukar da ita daukar karin sati biyu kashe zuwa kwata-kwata a kan dawowarsu ba.
Ya ce yana tsammanin abu ne mai wuya za su samu kudin fansar jirgin, kamar yadda ba a soke shi ba.
“Na lalace,” in ji shi ya shaida wa BBC.
“Ina da iyali a Spain wadanda ba su ga jikokinsu kawai ba tun lokacin Kirsimeti.”
Lois Stothard, daga Kudancin Yorkshire, ta shaida wa BBC cewa ta kama hutu zuwa Seville a matsayin abin mamaki ga saurayinta ranar haihuwar 30 - saboda tashi daga ranar Lahadi da safe - amma yanzu tana jin cewa ba za ta iya tafiya ba.
“Ni ma'aikacin mahimmanci ne - ni malami ne - kuma saurayina yana da alkawuran aiki don haka ba za mu iya yin kwata-kwata ba har tsawon kwanaki 14 idan muka dawo,” in ji ta.
“Ba za mu iya samun wani kudi ba kuma don canza kamfanin so ninka abin da na riga na biya a kudade.
Ina matukar jin kunya da damuwa yayin da muke cakuduwa da shirye shiryen tafiya.”
Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi su ne “tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka”
Washington - Sanata Ted Cruz na Texas ya zargi Kakakin Majalisa Nancy Pelosi da House Democrats da tura wani kunshin taimako na coronavirus wanda ke mayar da hankali kan “tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka” yayin da tattaunawa a mataki na gaba ke ci gaba.
A cikin wata hira da “Face the Nation” a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar tana fuskantar matsalolin biyu a lokaci guda: wata annoba ta duniya da ta yi ikirarin rayukan mutane fiye da 600,000 a duniya da kuma “cikakkiyar masifa ta tattalin arziki” a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya bayyana a kan “Face the Nation” gaban sanata, "yana “mayar da hankali ga ba daga cikin wadanda ba.”
“Manufofinta suna nuna tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka,” in ji Texas Republican.
“Kuma musamman ma, ka kalli takardar Naira tiriliyan 3 da take kokarin turawa, kawai tana fallasa kudi ne ga abokanta kuma ba a zahiri warware matsalar ba. Manufarmu ya kamata Amurkawa su so su dawo aiki. Suna so su iya azurta wa iyalinsu.”
'Yan majalisar dattijai Republicans da fadar White House sun shafe makon jiya suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan karo na hudu na martanin coronavirus, inda suke sa ran kashe dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikata na White House Mark Meadows da sakataren baitulmalin Steven Mnuchin sun gangara zuwa Capitol Hill don karin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar dattijai, kuma Mnuchin ya gaya wa Fox News a wata hira da aka yi ranar Lahadi an tsara cikakkun bayanai da za a bayyana daga shugaban masu rinjaye Mitch McConnell a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi damuwa ga masu shari'a - da kuma batun jayayya tsakanin 'yan Republicans da Democrats - shi ne karewar ingantaccen amfanin rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara tafiya a wannan karshen mako.
Duk da yake Democrats so “lokaci hudu” coronavirus kunshin don ci gaba da $600 bunkasa ga amfanin, Republicans suna kira a gare shi ya zama pared baya kuma suna jayayya da wasu Amurkawa suna yin karin daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke karbar ingantaccen aikin yi an biya su fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce ya yi magana da kananan masu kasuwanci a Texas wadanda ke fama da matsala wajen sake dawo da ma'aikata.
“Ko shakka babu, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyan su, a wasu lokutan, sau biyu da yawa kudi su zauna gida,” inji shi.
Cruz ya ce majalisa ya kamata ta mayar da hankali ga wucewa a dawo da lissafin da zai sa ya fi sauƙi ga Amurkawa su koma aiki ta hanyar sauƙaƙe haraji da dokoki a kan ƙananan kasuwanni: “maimakon kawai nuna triliyan daga ƙofar, lissafin dawowa zai dakatar da biyan haraji, wanda zai ba shi biyan kuɗi zuwa kowa da kowa a Amurka wanda ke aiki. Wannan a zahiri yana sa mutane su koma aiki,” inji shi.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci a makon da ya gabata kunshin agajin da ya hada da yanke haraji, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai kasance cikin dokokin ba, kamar yadda kudirin ya yi rashin karbuwa a tsakanin 'yan Republicans.
Mista Trump ya amince da yanke harajin zai kasance ba daga lissafi na gaba amma ya nemi fil zargi akan 'yan Democrats.
Cruz, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya ki amincewa da kudin kunshin mai zuwa, ya ce Lahadi ba ya cikin jirgi tare da awo daga 'yan uwansa Senate Republicans.
Amma kuma ya soki lissafin dala tiriliyan 3 da majalisar mai kula da democradiya ta shige a watan Mayu inda ya zargi abokan adawar sa na siyasa da gangan wajen aikata wani matakin da zai lalata shugaban kasar gabanin zaben watan Nuwamba.
“Manufar Democrats kawai ita ce kayar da Donald Trump, kuma sun yanke shawarar hanya mafi kyau don kayar da Donald Trump an rufe kowane kasuwanci a Amurka, rufe kowace makaranta a Amurka,” in ji shi.
“Ka sani, Nancy Pelosi tayi magana game da aiki maza da mata. Abin da ta ke ba da shawara shi ne kiyaye aiki maza da mata daga aiki.”
Rahul Gandhi Ya Yi Wa Mutane Kan Batun Rajasthan
Congress Rahul Gandhi ya tweeted wani bidiyo a yau yana yunkurin wayar da kan mutane kan BJP kan abubuwan da suka faru a Rajasthan.
Ta amfani da hashtag #SpeakUpForDemocracy, shi Hindia post ya bukaci mutane su “Hada kai da tayar da muryarmu don dimokuradiyya.”
Congress na shirin gudanar da zanga-zanga a fadin kasar a ranar Litinin kan halin da ake ciki a Rajasthan, inda gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot ke gwagwarmayar tsira.
Yayin da jam'iyyar ta ce za a gudanar da zanga-zangar ne a wajen Rashtrapati Bhavan, mazaunin shugaba Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyon, Majalisa ta zargi BJP da “Ripping up the constitution and rushe democradiya” yayin da daukacin kasar ke yaki da cutar coronavirus.
Ya yi haka a Madhya Pradesh, in ji majalisa.
“Muna bukatar a gaggauta gudanar da wani zaman majalisa wanda ke cikin hakkokinmu na mulki,” in ji jam'iyyar a cikin bidiyon.
Rajasthan Gwamna Kalraj Mishra ya juya shawarar daya gabatar domin fara wani zaman majalisa.
An mika wani na biyu yau wanda yace yana jarabawa.
Gwamnatin Mr Gehlot ta kasance cikin tsananin rikici bayan da mataimakinsa Sachin Pilot ya juya tawaye tare da kakkabe 'yan tawayen MLAs da ke goyon bayansa.
Jam'iyyar dai ta kasa rashin cancantar 'yan tawayen su kawo saukar da alamar mafi rinjaye a cikin taron.
Mr Pilot - wanda aka cire daga mukaminsa a cikin jam'iyyar da kuma gwamnati - an ba shi taimako na wucin gadi daga rashin cancanta daga Rajasthan High Court, wanda ya rike cewa Mai Magana ba zai iya daukar wani mataki ba har sai an yanke shawarar tambaya mafi girma game da ikonsa.
Za a ɗauki wannan tambaya gobe ta Kotun Koli, wadda kuma za ta yanke hukunci ko wata kotu za ta iya tsoma baki game da hukunce-hukuncen Kakakin Majalisar.
Majalisa ta tsaya ne kawai da alama mafi rinjaye a cikin majalisar wakilai ta 200.
Kungiyar Pilot ta yi ikirarin goyon bayan 30 MLAs, amma ya zuwa yanzu, shaidar ta nuna kawai 19.
BJP yana da 72 kuma ciki har da abokai da masu zaman kansu, yana tsaye a 97.
Idan kotu ta yanke hukunci bisa goyon bayan Mr Pilot, majalisa za ta iya rasa na biyu daga cikin gwamnatoci uku da ta kafa a jihohin da ke da zuciya bayan zaben 'yan majalisa na 2018.
A watan Maris, ya rasa gwamnatin Kamal da ke jagoranta a Madhya Pradesh bayan Jyotiraditya ScIndia ya shiga jam'iyyar BJP tare da 22 daga cikin jama'iyyarsa ta MLas.
An kama jami'an 'yan sandan Kenya bayan harbi miyagu a Garissa
An kama 'yan sanda biyu a Kenya dangane da wani harbi inda aka kashe mutane biyu.
Harbe-harben ya faru ne a kasuwar Soko Ng'ombe da ke gabashin karamar hukumar Garissa a ranar Asabar, yayin wata zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da kama wani mutum da ake zargi da kisan kai.
Mutanen biyun da aka kashe an bayyana su ne a matsayin Aden Abdi Madobe da Muhiyadin Adow Shibin.
Rundunar 'yan sandan Kenya ta kaddamar da bincike kan harbe-harben.
Zai hada da “bincike na bincike” na bindigogin jami'ai.
Garissa MP Aden Duale ya kira mutuwar “heinous” kuma ya hukunta “cin zarafin 'yan sanda” a wata sanarwa da aka fitar wa Facebook.
'Yan gwagwarmaya sun tayar da damuwa game da 'yan sanda a lokacin annoba.
A cewar Amnesty International, jami'an Kenya sun kashe mutane 21 tun watan Maris saboda gaza bin matakan rigakafin cutar coronavirus kamar su lankwasa da kuma sake-ka-saka.
Tun da farko a wannan watan 'yan sanda a babban birnin Nairobi sun harba gas mai hawaye kuma suka kama masu zanga-zanga da dama da ke shiga cikin watan Saba na shekara-shekara - wani taron zanga-zangar wadda aka fara shekaru 30 da suka wuce game da tsarin mulkin kaka-ni-shugaban kasa Daniel Arap Moi.
Masu ba da labari sun ce taron na wannan shekara ya ba da karin fushi a kan fashewar 'yan sanda a lokacin kulle Covid-19.
Shivraj Singh Chouhan A kan gwaji mai kyau
Madhya Pradesh Babban Minista Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda a ranar Asabar ya tabbatar da cewa ya gwada tabbatacce ga COVID-19, tweeted Lahadi da safe ya ce yana “lafiya” kuma ya bayar da yabo ga ma'aikatan gaba a yaki da cutar coronavirus.
Babban Ministan ya kuma maimaita gargadin da ya yi daga jiya, lokacin da ya bukaci mutane da su bi jagorori, kamar kuncin rayuwa da kuma amfani da mayukan fuska.
“Ina lafiya, abokaina. Ƙaddamar da mayaƙan coronavirus, waɗanda ba su da haɗari da rayukansu, yana da kyau. Ina gaisawa da dukkan mayaƙan coronavirus na jihar,” Mr Chouhan tweeted daga asibitin Bhopal na Chirayu, inda aka shigar da shi jiya.
“Tsaya mita biyu, wanke hannayenka akai-akai kuma ku sa masks na fuska - waɗannan su ne manyan makamai da muke da su don kauce wa coronavirus. Ina roko ga dukkan mutane - ku yi amfani da wadannan makamai domin kanku da kuma 'yan uwanku,” inji shi.
“Dukkanku ku yi hankali, ku zauna lafiya da lafiya. Wannan shine abinda nake addu'a ga Allah,” Mr Chouhan ya kara da cewa.
A ranar Asabar Mr Chouhan ya tweeted cewa ya gwada tabbatacce ga cutar duk da kokarinsa na kauce wa kamuwa da cutar kuma ya yi gargadin cewa “kawai rashin kulawa ne ke gayyatar cutar coronavirus.”
Tweeting a wannan safiya Mr Chouhan ya ce duk da barazanar kamuwa da cutar akwai “babu bukatar tsoro” kuma ya bukaci wadanda ke nuna alamu da su samu kansu gwaji.
“Idan kana dauke da cutar, babu bukatar tsoro. Kada ku ɓoye bayyanar cututtuka amma ku gaya wa likitoci nan da nan, don haka za a iya fara magani. Yin magani na dai-dai zai sa ku lafiya,” inji shi.
