Indiya ta yi rubuce-rubuce a COVID-19 a makonnin da suka gabata, tare da sabbin kararraki 45,000 da aka gano a kowace rana tun daga ranar 23 ga watan Yuli.
Jimlar adadin wadanda aka tabbatar da cutar coronavirus yana saurin gabatowa 14 lakh; daga cikin wadannan fiye da 4.67 lakh suna aiki ne kuma sama da 32,000 suna da nasaba da cutar.
Guguwa a lokuta, wanda ya dace da shakatawa mai ban al'ajabi na jagororin kulle a yankunan da ba a yarda da su ba na kasar, ya sa Indiya ta zama na uku a jerin kasashe mafi yawan abin da ya shafa.
Sai dai Amurka (lokuta 41.78 lakh) da Brazil (lokuta 23.94 lakh) sun fi muni.
Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia ya kira sabon PM, don kafa gwamnati a cikin wata guda
An nada ministan cikin gida na Tunisia Hichem Mechichi domin samar da gwamnati mai zuwa, ofishin shugaban ya ce, a tsakanin tashe-tashen hankula na siyasa a tsakanin manyan jam'iyyu a kasar ta Arewacin Afirka.
Lauyan mai shekaru 42 ya yi nasara da Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus a matsayin firayim minista a farkon wannan watan.
Sai dai Mechichi bai kasance daya daga cikin sunayen da masu rike da mukaman siyasa suka gabatar wa shugaba Kais Saeed.
A cikin wata sanarwa da ta biyo bayan sanarwar ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai “yi aiki domin samar da gwamnatin da ta dace da tsammanin daukacin 'yan Tunisiya.”
An yaba wa Tunisia a matsayin labarin nasara mai ban mamaki ga sauyin mulkin dimokuradiyya bayan da 'yan tawaye na yankin Larabawa suka bullo da juyin juya halin 2011.
Amma shugabanninta sun yi gwagwarmayar cimma tsammanin mutanen Tunisiya da tuni tattalin arziki ya yi batan dabo ta hanyar rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe mutane kusan 50 ta kuma kamu da cutar fiye da 1,400 a Tunisia.
Kazalika kasancewarsa ministan cikin gida a gwamnati mai barin gado, Mechichi ya kasance mai bayar da shawara ga shugaba Saeed, mai kula da harkokin shari'a.
A baya ya kasance shugaban ma'aikata a ma'aikatar sufuri sannan kuma ya yi aiki a ma'aikatar jin dadin jama'a.
Yanzu yana da wata guda don samar da gwamnati, wanda zai fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa na majalisa kuma zai bukaci cikakken rinjaye don samun nasara.
Rashin cewa, za a rushe majalisar dokoki kuma za a gudanar da sabon zabe cikin watanni uku.
A zaben karshe da aka gudanar a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta zo a saman amma ta fadi gajere da rinjaye kuma daga karshe ta amince da shiga gwamnatin hadin gwiwa.
Fakhfakh ta murabus a ranar 15 ga Yuli, bayan kasa da watanni biyar a ofishin, ya yi barazanar sake haifar da mummunar siyasa a cikin al'umma yayin da yake fama da matsalar tattalin arziki na annoba.
Murabus din ya zurfafa jayayya ta siyasa da Ennahdha a kan zargin da Fakhfakh na rikice-rikice na sha'awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaba mai barin gado 47 da Ennahdha ta yi tsami tun bayan zaben majalisar dokokin na watan Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a wannan rana da jam'iyyar ta gabatar da wani motsi mara amincewa da shi.
Ennahdha ya fara zabar wani mai zaman kansa ga firayim minista, amma ya kasa lashe goyon bayan majalisa, yana jagorantar shugaban ya kira tsohon ministan kudi Fakhfakh don mukamin.
Da ya fuskanci tsaikon sabbin zabuka, Ennahdha ya amince ya shiga gwamnatin hadin kai.
Mota ta hanyar taron jama'a, mai zanga-zanga ya harbe a Colorado
AUROA, Colo. (AP) - Wata mota ta kife ta wurin taron jama'a kuma an harbi wani mai zanga-zanga a unguwar Denver da ke unguwar Aurora a lokacin zanga-zangar nuna rashin adalci ga launin fata.
Sashin 'Yan Sandan Aurora ya fada a Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar suna tafiya ne a Interstate 225 ranar Asabar a lokacin da wata motar hawa ta ratsa ta.
'Yan sanda sunce wani mai zanga-zanga ya harba makami, ya harba akalla mutum daya da aka kai shi wani asibiti cikin koshin lafiya.
Hukumomi sunce an kamo motar kuma suna bincike.
Masu zanga-zanga sun kuma fasa tagogi zuwa gidan kotun kuma an fara barin wuta a wani ofis, in ji 'yan sanda.
An ayyana wani haramtaccen taro kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zanga su bar yankin, hukumomi suka ce.
An ƙarfafa tashin hankali a zanga-zangar da aka yi kwanan nan game da rashin adalci na launin fata tun lokacin da aka tura jami'an tarayya don yin zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun bayyana bore a Seattle ranar Asabar.
Masu zanga-zangar sun yi sandiyar mutuwar 25 ga watan Mayu kan mutuwar George Floyd, wani bakar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan da wani jami'in farin kaya ya rike shi a kasa tare da yi masa gwiwa a wuyansa, sun kuma yi hasashen wasu ababe da suka haddasa tashin hankalin 'yan sanda.
A Colorado, masu zanga-zanga sun yi ta jan hankali game da mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka dakatar da shi yayin da yake tafiya a wani titin Aurora a watan Agustan 2019 bayan wani mai kira 911 ya ruwaito shi a matsayin m.
'Yan sanda sun sanya shi a cikin wani chokehold, kuma paramidics gudanar da 500 milligrams na ketamine, mai magani, don kwantar da shi.
Ya shiga bugun zuciya, daga baya aka ayyana kwakwalwa matacce kuma aka cire tallafin rayuwa.
Famously share Lake Tahoe ya gurɓata ta hanyar sauyin yanayi
Kudancin Lake Tahoe, California - Duk da annoba, har ma a mako guda, mutane har yanzu suna taron Paparoma Beach a Lake Tahoe.
“Ina son zango da ciwon hawan keke da kuma yin iyo a tafkin,” inji wata yarinya mai suna Dakota.
“Wannan wani abu ne mai kyau kowa yana son ziyarta,” in ji Emerica Benitas.
Wanda shine dalilin da ya sa kasuwancin Matt Meunier ya nutse har yanzu yana da karfi, har ma a cikin wani annoba.
Yace yana ganin “tsafta kwarai. Tafkin Tahoe shi ne tafkin mafi tsabta, mafi ban mamaki, ina tsammanin, a kasar.”
Yanzu mummunan labari: Tafkin Tahoe ba shi da tsabta, ba kamar yadda ya kasance a bayyane ba, kamar yadda ya kasance lokacin da ya koma nan sama da shekaru biyu da suka wuce.
“Abinda muke lura da shi sosai yana ƙasa a kan duwatsu,” in ji Meunier.
“Kana samun wannan algae mai ban mamaki a kan duwatsu.”
Canjin yanayi, masana kimiyya sun yi imani, ya shafi yanayin zafin jiki na ruwa kuma ta haka, tsabta.
Kuma mutane miliyan 15 sun ziyarci tafkin a kowace shekara - tare da datti da suka bar.
Meunier ya ce nutsewa tafiye-tafiye don tsaftace sama da kasa na tafkin sami tsohon shara.
“Kuma idan na ce tsohuwar shara, ina nufin '60s, '70s,” in ji Meunier.
“Giya gwangwani, soda gwangwani, gwangwani na coci daga tsohuwar kwanakin.”
Masana kimiyya na lura da tsabtar tafkin Tahoe a kowace shekara ta hanyar saukar da wani farin faifai, sai su auna yadda nisan sauka za su iya ganinsa.
UC Davis farfesa Geoff Schladow yace yana da “muhimmiyar alama ta yadda lafiyar tafkin yake.”
Lokacin da aka auna a bara, tsabtace tafkin ya kai kimanin kafa 80.
Wannan yana nufin za ka ga wannan faifan 80 ƙafa ƙasa.
Amma, la'akari da wannan, game da shekaru 20 da suka wuce, tsabta na tafkin ya kasance ƙafafun 100.
Wannan shine yadda masana kimiyya ke kokarin juyawa.
Amma suna yaki da tasirin sauyin yanayi, ci gaba a kusa da tafkin da wani abu da aka kara wa tafkin a shekarun 1960: Wani dan kankanin shrimp da aka kawo don ciyar da kifi.
Bai yi aiki ba.
“Da zarar shrimp ya shigo, babu zato ba tsammani babu masu tsabtace halitta a cikin tafkin,” in ji Schladow.
Hakazalika kalubale suna fuskantar tabkuna da jikkunan ruwa a duniya.
“Darasi a nan shi ne, idan ba za ka iya yi ba a Tahoe, to wane fata ke nan ga dukan koguna da iskoki da koguna da koguna da ke kewaye da kasar nan da ba za su taba samun irin wannan mataki na hankali ba, irin matakin albarkatu?” Schladow ya ce.
Meunier ya ce yana “fatan” saboda “idan akwai rufi na azurfa na annoba, ina tsammanin ya nuna cewa yanayi zai dawo kuma ya warkar da kansa idan muka dogara da wannan matsa lamba, cewa mutum matsa lamba, kashe shi kuma ya bar shi ya faru. Akwai hujjoji a can yanzu.”
Ma'aurata MACED a filin shakatawa na kare California don kada a saka masks na fuska yayin cin abincin rana (bidiyo) - Labaran RT Amurka
Akwai masu-shaming sannan akwai cike a kan hari.
A California ma'aurata suna cin abincin rana tare da kwikwiyo a wani kare shakatawa fuskanci na biyu, lokacin da wani irate mace barkono ya fesa su don ƙin rufe sama... yayin cin abinci.
Ash O'Brien da miji Jarett Kelley sun ce sun kama cizon da za su ci a wurin shakatawa na kare Dusty Rhodes da ke San Diego a ranar Alhamis, tare da jinyar su mai watanni uku a cikin tow.
Biyu suna da masks su ci abinci, lokacin da “bazuwar tsohuwar uwargidan” ta kusanci, kiran su “ƙuƙwalwa” don kada ku rufe, ko da yake “ba za ku iya sa mask ba kuma ku ci a lokaci guda.”
O'Brien ya gaya wa matar ta bar wurin shakatawa kuma ta daina cin zarafinta, a wani lokaci matar ta batar da wata iya macce a ma'aurata.
Hoton bidiyon da aka kama daga mai bystander ya fara da Kelley yana kokawa da fesa zai iya daga mace, da kuma samun kashi na macce a cikin fuska don matsalolin sa.
Za a iya jin O'Brien yana kuka a bango yayin da maharan ke tafiya tare da karnukanta.
O'Brien ya raba bidiyon a Facebook kuma ya fadawa ABC 10 cewa tana son ganin matar “tafi kurkuku.”
Masks fuska suna da muhimmanci a fadin jihar California, har ma a cikin iska mai iska.
Wadannan masks za a iya cire su kawai a wasu lokutan, ciki har da lokacin cin abinci ko sha.
Duk da haka, babu inda a cikin jagororin coronavirus na jihar ya yi hakan yana cewa masu amfani da makamai marasa mutuwa don tilasta wannan manufar.
Ko a zamanin yanzu na “sham-shaming,” har yanzu laifin ɗauke da hukuncin tarar $1,000 ko kuma har zuwa shekaru uku a gidan yarin jihar.
Scotland-Ingila Union Chain Bridge yana da shekaru 200
Wata gada da ta hada Scotland da Ingila ta mayar da shekaru 200 gabanin gyaran fam miliyan £10m.
Ƙungiyar Union Chain Bridge ta tsallaka Kogin Tweed daga Fishwick a cikin iyakokin Scottish zuwa Horncliffe a Northumberland.
Lokacin da aka buɗe a 1820, ita ce gadar dakatar da ƙarfe mafi tsawo a duniya tare da tsawon 449ft (137m).
Har ila yau, ita ce gadar farko ta mota irinta a Birtaniya.
Gadar dai an zanta da jami'in kamfanin Royal Navy na Ingila Capt Samuel Brown.
Ya yi sintiri kuma ya samar da sarkokin ƙarfe da aka yi masa bayan an yi masa hasarar jiragen ruwa na Royal Nadal wanda ya karye kyauta daga igiyoyi.
Abokai na Ƙungiyar Chain Bridge da Cibiyar Injiniyoyi (Ice) Scotland sun kasance suna nuna alamar tsallake-tsallake.
Robert Hunter, na ƙungiyar abokai, ya ce: “Wannan shi ne ainihin ɗaya daga cikin gadoji mafi tarihi a duniya da kuma wani injiniya mai ban sha'awa.
“Mun shirya wasu shagulgulan bikin ne domin nuna bukukuwa, amma abin takaici sai da aka dakatar da su.
“Duk da haka, gaskiyar cewa aiki ba da daɗewa ba za a fara a kan £10m gyara shi ne ranar haihuwar mafi kyau a yanzu kuma zai tabbatar da ƙarni da za su zo za su iya jin daɗin gadar a duk ƙawarta.”
Daraktan Ice Scotland Hannah Smith ya bayyana gadar a matsayin wani ɓangare na “wanda ba shi da kyau” na kayan aikin injiniya na Scotland.
Ta ce: “Mun san shi sanannen duniya ne a kan haka kuma yana da kyau cewa aikin zai fara jima a kan gyara shi.”
Salmonella annobar cutar sickens 212 mutane a jihohi 23
Yuli 25 (UPI) — Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafi suna bincike akan wani barkewar cutar salmonella da ya cutar da mutane 212 a jihohi 23.
A cikin wata sanarwar manema labarai da kafar yada labarai ta CDC ta fitar ta bayyana cewa mutane 87 ne suka kamu da rashin lafiya tun sabunta ta karshe a ranar Talata.
Hukumar tace mutane sun fara nuna alamun da ke da nasaba da wani nau'in salmonella, wanda zai iya daukar makonni biyu zuwa hudu don nuna alamun cututtuka, tsakanin 19 ga watan Yuni da 11 ga watan Yuli.
Mutane talatin da daya sun kamu da cutar tun lokacin da annobar ta fara, amma ba a samu rahoton bullar cutar ba.
A cewar CDC, ba a gano takamaiman tushe ga nau'in salmonella ba.
Bai bayar da wani shawara game da cin abinci ko cinye wasu abinci ba, ba kuma masu sayar da kayan da za su iya sayar da kayan da aka gurbata ba.
Oregon yana da mafi yawan lokuta na salmonella, tare da 51 cututtuka, tare da Utah bayan kusa da 40 rahotanni.
Salmonella kwayoyin cuta ce, rashin abinci wanda ke haifar da cututtuka miliyan 1.35, 26,500 asibiti, da kuma mutuwar 420 a kowace shekara, a cewar CDC.
Mafi yawan bayyanar cututtuka na kamuwa da cutar salmonella shine zawo, zazzabi, da kuma ƙwayar ciki, wanda zai iya farawa tsakanin sa'o'i shida da kwanaki shida bayan daukan hotuna.
Rashin lafiya yakan yi kwanaki hudu zuwa bakwai, kuma mafi yawan mutane na warkewa ba tare da magani ba, amma wasu lokuta na bukatar garzaya da su asibiti.
United, Chelsea zuwa CL; Bournemouth, Watford sauka daga EPL
Manchester United da Chelsea da suka cancanci cin kofin zakarun Turai a karawar da Leicester ke yi a wasan dab da na karshe na kakar wasannin Premier League a ranar Lahadi, yayin da Bournemouth da Watford suka sake lashewa don kawo karshen zaman shekaru biyar a saman jirgin.
United ta ci 2-0 a Leicester ta zira kwallaye a raga ta hannun Bruno Fernandes da Jesse Lingard su ba kungiyar Ole Gunnar Solskjaer a matsayi na uku a karawar.
Chelsea ta doke Wolverhampton 2-0 bayan zira kwallo da taimakon Mason Mount da kammala a gasar cin kofin zakarun turai na hudu dana karshe wato Champions league cancantar matsayi sama da Leicester, wadda ta kasance a sahun hudu mafi yawa a kakar wasa ta bana.
Leicester, a maimakon haka, za ta buga wasa a Europa League tare da Tottenham, wadda ta ja 1-1 a Crystal Palace don tsare wuri na shida - sama da Wolverhampton a kan bambancin kwallo.
Yaƙi don kauce wa sauran wurare biyu da suka rage sun tafi da waya kamar yadda Aston Villa ta sha a cikin minti na 84, ya amince da minti daya daga baya, sa'an nan kuma a kan don 1-1 zana a West Ham don tsira.
Kaftin Jack Grealish ne ya zura wa Villa kwallo a raga a abin da zai iya zama wasan sa na karshe ga kulob din sa na boy
Bournemouth ta yi abin da ya kamata ta yi kuma ta doke Everton, 3-1, amma ta kare maki daya a bayan Villa.
Watford kuma aka sake rantsar da shi a matsayin kungiyar wasan dab da na karshe bayan rasa 3-2 a Arsenal.
Manchester City ta zira kwallo ta 100 domin fafatawar da ci 5-0 a wasan karshe da Norwich mai ra'ayin rikau, wasan da ya yi alama ta karshe a gasar Premier League ta lallasa David Silva bayan shekaru 10 tare da City.
Kevin De Bruyne ya sami rikodin 20th taimako na kakar wasan kuma ya sha sau biyu.
Liverpool ta kawo karshen kakar wasa ta bana da ci 3-1 a gidan Newcastle kuma ta gama a club-record maki 99.
Har ila yau, Southampton ta doke Sheffield United 3-1, tare da Danny Ings da ya zira kwallo 22 a kakar wasa ta bana.
Hakan ya bar masa daya bayan dan wasan Leicester wato Jamie Vardy, wanda ya lashe Golden Boot a matsayin dan wasan league mafi girma.
Tony Blair yayi wasali kada ya daina tunani a siyasar Birtaniya duk da tsananin Brexit backlash
Tony Blair ya yi alkawarin ba zai daina shiga tsakani a siyasar Birtaniya ba, bayan tsananin koma baya ga shigarsa cikin jam'iyyar Labour da masu fafutukar hana karya lagon karya.
Mr Blair, wanda ya fita daga ofishin fiye da shekaru goma, ya gaya wa Sophy Ridge a kan Sky News cewa ba zai “taba” daina magana a cikin siyasar Birtaniya ba.
Duk da haka, adadi na siyasa mai rikitarwa ya yarda “mutane da yawa suna kallon wannan suna iya tunanin ya kamata in daina magana game da abubuwa.”
Sophy Ridge ya gaya wa Mr Blair: “Kullum ina samun ma'ana ba za ka iya kawar da kanka daga siyasa ba.”
“Kullum kuna wallafa rahotanni game da coronavirus ko kuma kuna zuwa tare da muhawara akan Brexit.”
“Ni dai ina mamaki idan mutane suka yi tunani, me ya sa bayan shekaru goma da zama PM, har yanzu kana kokarin shiga harkar siyasa?”
“Shin lokaci ba ne da za a dauki lokaci ba, ka zagaya filin wasan golf.”
Tsohon firaministan ya karyata wannan kuma yayi alkwarin tsayawa a siyasar Birtaniya muddin zai iya.
Ya ce: “Ba wani abu da nake son yi ba. Mutane da yawa da ake kallo zasu iya tunanin hakan shine ainihin abinda ya kamata yayi kuma ya daina magana akan abubuwa, amma na damu da kasar.”
“Muna cikin babban lokacin canji a duniya da kuma cibiyar da na gina ayyuka a duniya.”
“Na san nayi wani abu da firayim ministoci na baya basu yi ba amma nan gaba na hango mutane da yawa zasu yi kokarin yi.”
Tun da farko a hirar da aka yi, Mr Blair ya ce har yanzu Birtaniya da EU na iya sauka kan yarjejeniyar Brexit kafin karshen shekara.
Ya ce: “Za su iya sauka da wata yarjejeniya. Amma hatta yarjejeniyar da muka kasa za ta zama mummuna.”
“Hakan zai zama mai kyau ga Turai saboda zai ba da izinin sauƙin cinikayya a kayayyaki amma yana hana mana sosai a kan batun ayyuka.”
Tsohon shugaban kwadago ya kuma shaidawa Sky News cewa Birtaniya za ta zauna tare da COVID-19, ba kawar da ita ba, don makomar da za a iya gani.
A lokacin da ya yi wa Kargil heroes, PM Narendra Modi Ya Ce Pakistan Ta Yi Kokarin “Backstab” Indiya
Pakistan ta yi kokarin “backstab” Indiya Duk da yunkurin da ta ke yi na ci gaba da sada zumunci, Firaminista Narendra Modi ya ce yau a jinjina wa sojojin da suka yi a bikin cika shekaru 21 da yakin Kargil.
A cikin jawabinsa na rediyo na wata-wata Mann ki Baat, PM Modi ya ce “Pakistan ta yi wannan mummunar ta'ada tare da shirin kama kasar Indiya da kuma karkatar da rikice-rikicen cikin gida da take ci gaba da yi.”
“Pakistan na da kwarin gwiwa na kokarin zama kasar Indiya kuma ta karkatar da hankali daga rashin kwanciyar hankali na cikin gida,” in ji shi.
“A lokacin, Indiya na kokarin inganta dangantaka da Pakistan. Amma kamar yadda ake fada, mugunta dabi'a ce ta yaki kowa ba tare da dalili ba. Mutane masu wannan dabi'a ne kawai za su iya tunanin aikata mugunta har ma ga wadanda ke kokarin yi musu alheri. Hakan ya sa Pakistan ta mara wa Indiya baya duk da yunkurin Indiya na kulla alaka da juna,” inji shi..
“Za ka iya tunanin, abokan gaba sun yi sama a kan duwatsu yayin da sojojin mu ke fada da su daga kasa. Amma babban dabi'u da gaskiya na rundunarmu sun ci nasara a kan duwatsu,” ya kara da cewa.
“Mun gode da karfin gwiwar sojojin mu, Indiya ta nuna karfi sosai a Kargil,” in ji PM Modi, yana tunawa da ziyarar da ya kai yankin.
Ana bikin Kargil Diwas a kowace shekara, yana nuna ranar da Sojojin Indiya suka sake kama dukkanin gine-ginen Indiya a Kargil na Ladakh wanda sojojin Pakistan suka mamaye shekaru 21 da suka gabata.
A ranar 26 ga watan Yuli na shekarar 1999, rundunar sojan kasar ta sanar da samun nasarar kwace “Operation Vijay.”
Kusan kusan watanni uku a cikin tsauni na Ladakh ya yi ikirarin rayukan fiye da 500 sojojin Indiya.
Tun da farko a yau, ministan tsaro Rajnath Singh, da karamin minista Shripad Naik, Babban Jami'in Tsaro Janar Bipin Rawat, Babban Jami'in Soja Janar M Naravane, Air Chief Marshal R K S Bhadauria da kuma Navy Chief Admiral Karambir Singh ma sun biya kudin bautar kasar Amar Jawan Jyoti.
A shekarun da suka gabata tun lokacin Kargil, dangantakar Indiya-Pakistan ta yi tsami biyo bayan jerin ayyukan ta'addanci.
Indiya ta dage cewa tattaunawa da ta'addanci ba zai iya tafiya da hannu ba kuma Pakistan na bukatar rarraba duk sansanonin ta'addanci da ke aiki daga kasarta.
