Kanye West ya shafi neman gafarar jama'a ga matar Kim Kardashian bayan wahayin aure
Kanye West ya nemi gafarar matar Kim Kardashian don zuwa jama'a tare da “al'amari mai zaman kansa.”
Mai rafin ya bayyana a yayin wani abin da ya faru a South Carolina cewa ma'auratan sun dauke abortar da yaransu na farko.
Biyo bayan mako mai cike da takaddama inda ya yi jerin da'awar akan matarsa da iyalanta, yanzu haka West ta tweeted wani uzuri.
Har ila yau, jaridar West ta biya ziyara a asibiti sa'o'i bayan da Justin Bieber ya ziyarci shi a ranch dinsa a Wyoming.
Ya ce: “Ina so in nemi gafara ga matata Kim saboda tafi jama'a da wani abu da ya kasance abu mai zaman kansa.
