Ya kuma ce ya yi kokari ya saki Kardashian West, wanda ya yi aure a shekarar 2014.
A cikin tsoro ga tunanin mijinta, Kardashian West, mahaifiyar 'ya'yanta hudu na Yamma, ta ba da wata sanarwa mai tsawo da ke cewa ita da iyalinta sun kasance “marasa karfi” don shiga tsakani kuma ya tunatar da magoya bayan da yake da cutar bipolar.
Ta ce: “Shi mutum ne mai tsananin hankali amma mai rikitarwa wanda a saman matsin lamba na kasancewa mai zane da kuma baki, wanda ya dandana radadin asarar mahaifiyarsa, kuma dole ne ya magance matsi da kadaici da ke kara tabarbarewarsa ta bi-polar.”
Ta kara da cewa ba ta tattauna yanayinsa ba a baya saboda tana “matukar kare wa 'ya'yanmu da Kanye hakkin sirri idan ya zo lafiyarsa.”
Ta kara da cewa: “Amma a yau, ina jin kamar ya kamata in yi tsokaci a kansa saboda lalata da rashin tunani game da lafiyar kwakwalwa.”
West ya yi ikirarin zubar da ciki a lokacin wani taron a ranar 19 ga watan Yuli.
